{"tid":2443601,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"60歲女子嚴X儀龍蝦灣遇溺身亡","createTime":"2021-03-12T07:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T07:34:54.000Z","uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"501939b1002337be31254e98150a0a7de1cc4df8","tid":2443601,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210312/s00001/1615532515335/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210312%2Fs00001%2F1615532515335%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=68d91197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210312%2Fs00001%2F1615532515335%2F&h=9770e335\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210312/s00001/1615532515335/</a><br />\n<br />\n中午12時50分，一名女子於清水灣龍蝦灣對開約100米海面浮潛時遇溺，其他泳客見狀把她救起，惟女事主已陷入昏迷，救援人員到場把事主送住西貢對面海水警基地，再由救護車送院搶救，惜終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n女事主60歲嚴X儀，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71596a5434b9a47ebcd0c6f590b8caedeff085eb","tid":2443601,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe9a8ab0b4582d526cd83b04c1ff21bfc647476","tid":2443601,"uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"X舜儀 ?"},{"pid":